sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User (Browser)
    participant SPA as React SPA<br/>(main.tsx)
    participant OIDC as paycor-oidc-client<br/>UserManager
    participant STS as Paycor STS<br/>/sts/v1/common
    participant IFRAME as silent_renew.html<br/>(hidden iframe)
    participant BE as Express Backend<br/>(server.js)
    participant APIm as Paycor APIm<br/>Gateway
    participant SVC as Teammate.Service<br/>(.NET / Agent)

    Note over U,SPA: 1. Initial Load & Login
    U->>SPA: GET /teammate/*
    SPA->>SPA: Route = authenticated?<br/>AuthenticatedRoutes mounts
    SPA->>OIDC: useAuthentication(userManagerSettings)
    OIDC->>STS: Redirect to /sts/v1/common<br/>response_type=token<br/>client_id=TeammateAgentUI
    STS-->>U: Login UI (if no session)
    U->>STS: Credentials
    STS-->>OIDC: Redirect w/ #access_token
    OIDC-->>SPA: status='success', user.access_token

    Note over SPA,OIDC: 2. Privilege Enrichment
    SPA->>OIDC: UserManager.getUserByAccessToken(token)
    OIDC->>APIm: GET user + privileges<br/>(Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key)
    APIm-->>OIDC: User with hasPrivilege()
    OIDC-->>SPA: Enriched User
    SPA->>SPA: hasPrivilege(2253)?<br/>yes → App / no → ForbiddenPage
    SPA->>SPA: UserProvider stores user<br/>(context + module-level)

    Note over SPA,IFRAME: 3. Background Silent Renew (automaticSilentRenew)
    OIDC->>IFRAME: Load silent_renew.html in iframe
    IFRAME->>STS: signinSilentCallback()<br/>prompt=none
    STS-->>IFRAME: New access_token
    IFRAME-->>OIDC: Token refreshed
    OIDC-->>SPA: user.access_token updated

    Note over U,SVC: 4. Authenticated API Call (axios)
    SPA->>SPA: getAxiosInstance()<br/>reads getCurrentUser()
    SPA->>APIm: GET/POST ...<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token><br/>Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key<br/>Cookie (withCredentials)
    APIm->>SVC: Forward (validated)
    SVC-->>APIm: 200 / data
    APIm-->>SPA: Response
    SPA-->>U: Render

    Note over SPA,SVC: 5. CopilotKit Agent Call (chat)
    SPA->>BE: POST /api/copilotkit/.../connect<br/>Authorization, Cookie,<br/>Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key, Time-Zone
    BE->>BE: Middleware:<br/>setThreadCredentials(threadId, headers)
    BE->>BE: createHttpAgentWithAuth(req)<br/>forwards 4 auth headers
    BE->>APIm: Agent run/connect<br/>(auth forwarded)
    APIm->>SVC: AG-UI stream
    SVC-->>APIm: Events
    APIm-->>BE: Stream
    BE->>SVC: GET /threads/{id} history<br/>(stored credentials)
    SVC-->>BE: Messages
    BE-->>SPA: AG-UI events replayed
    SPA-->>U: Chat UI

    Note over BE,STS: 6. Service-to-Service (backend only)
    BE->>STS: POST /sts/v2/common/token<br/>grant_type=client_credentials<br/>client_id=TeammateService
    STS-->>BE: access_token (machine)
    BE->>APIm: Prompt blob upload<br/>Bearer <machine_token>

    Note over U,SVC: 7. Public JWT Flow (feedback / cancel)
    U->>SPA: GET /feedback/submit?token=<jwt>
    SPA->>SPA: isValidJWTFormat(token)?
    SPA->>APIm: GET /f/submit?token=...<br/>Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key only<br/>(NO bearer)
    APIm->>SVC: Validate JWT signature
    SVC-->>APIm: success / duplicate / error
    APIm-->>SPA: Response
    SPA-->>U: /feedback/thanks | /duplicate | /error

    Note over SPA,APIm: 8. Error Handling
    APIm-->>SPA: 401 / 403
    SPA->>SPA: errorMessage_401 / _403<br/>→ redirect or ForbiddenPage
